  <Team
    name="Social Entrepreneur Support"
    description="Our Social Entrepreneur Support team are the people delivering market leading support to social entrepreneurs through one-to-one coaching and enabling peer to peer connections to other award winners and alumni. We're here to help you from the start your journey with us so you may also receive support from us to help you access our awards (grant funding) if you have additional needs when you apply."
    positions={positions}
  />

  <Team
    name="Delivery and Investment"
    description="Designing and delivering market-leading support with and alongside our partners, supporters and colleagues. We are focussed on breaking down the barriers faced by social entrepreneurs. This includes accessing specialist expertise through our partnership work, and accessing the right investment through the Growth Impact Fund."
